
Memorandum to ISDA's Documentation and Collateral Committees:

To receive a copy of the March 12th draft of the 2001 ISDA Margin Provisions
and the blackline compared to the January 22 draft, please send an e-mail to
documents@isda.org with a reference in the subject heading to "DRAFTMP2" and
a copy will be sent to you by automatic reply e-mail.  Please note that this
process is entirely automatic and that ISDA staff will NOT review incoming
e-mails.

